{
  "stem": "23428.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was sort of a cabbage-- cabbage soup [? mess. ?] There was always a great amusement when people found a-- a-- a fiber of meat in it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it was great exhilaration if they discovered a fiber of meat in it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- only on rarest of occasions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, it was-- it was clearly, you know, I don't know how many calories.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the-- the operation of the work camp, to my mind, clearly had the purpose of utilizing the muscle power of the people involved to the-- for the benefit of the-- of Germany and its industry and as long as possible.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, you put-- you put 1,000 calories a day in, and you take 4,000 out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And under those circumstances, you know, you could plot if you had-- had graph paper, you could have plotted how long you were going to stay, which, I think-- I think that's-- it's about a year.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and I'm extremely suspicious of people who was-- who were in concentration camps for longer periods than that, at least the concentration camps that I knew, because it was impossible, unless you-- you had-- you had acquired rank.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the only way you could acquire rank was to-- was to be a traitor on your fellow prisoners, you know, which was very obvious.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Every night-- you see, every night, the-- the evening ended with what-- an institution that's called the appell.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The appell meant that everybody had to line up in-- in rows of 10 and be counted.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the official purpose of this thing was to make sure nobody escaped.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
